OL,3,CAirport trial judge referred Nigel
OL,4,CFarage comments to Attorney General
OL,6,FA judge has claimed comments made by
OL,7,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage during
OL,8,Fthe first Manchester Airport assault
OL,9,Ftrial could have been deemed contempt
OL,10,Fof court.
OL,12,FMr Farage leader spoke out about the
OL,13,Fcase as the initial trial of Mohammed
OL,14,FFahir Amaaz, 21, and Muhammad Amaad,
OL,15,F26, was ongoing at Liverpool Crown
OL,16,FCourt.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
