OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780081925
OL,3,CAirport trial judge referred Nigel
OL,4,CFarage comments to Attorney General
OL,6,FOn 21 June, he told a press
OL,7,Fconference: "In a system of two-tier
OL,8,Fpolicing, under two-tier justice,
OL,9,Funder two-tier Keir, has really taken
OL,10,Fhold.
OL,12,F"You only have to look at the
OL,13,Freluctance to prosecute those violent
OL,14,Fthugs in Manchester Airport who beat
OL,15,Fup the police officers.
OL,26,@oD@MOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
