OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780081925
OL,3,CAirport trial judge referred Nigel
OL,4,CFarage comments to Attorney General
OL,6,F"It took months and months for any
OL,7,Fprosecution to be brought, and I
OL,8,Fsuspect the reason that it happened is
OL,9,Fbecause Reform said if they didn't we
OL,10,Fwould take out our own private
OL,11,Fprosecution.
OL,13,FLater that day ` and not in front of
OL,14,Fthe jury ` Judge Neil Flewitt KC said
OL,15,Fa member of the public had informed
OL,16,Fhim over lunch about the comments from
OL,17,FMr Farage.
OL,19,FJudge Flewitt said: "It would have
OL,20,Fbeen better not said. That's probably
OL,21,Fan understatement."
OL,26,@nD@AOU{D@UOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
