OL,3,CAirport trial judge referred Nigel
OL,4,CFarage comments to Attorney General
OL,6,FEarlier in the trial he rejected an
OL,7,Fapplication from the defence teams to
OL,8,Fthrow out the case on the grounds that
OL,9,FAmaaz and Amaad could not have a fair
OL,10,Ftrial because of ongoing prejudicial
OL,11,Fcomments on social media.
OL,13,FJudge Flewitt said: "I don't mean in
OL,14,Fany way to downplay the
OL,15,Finappropriateness of what was said (by
OL,16,FFarage) but it doesn't seem to add
OL,17,Fanything to the material that I
OL,18,Fconsidered last week."
OL,26,@uD@UOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
