OL,3,CAirport trial judge referred Nigel
OL,4,CFarage comments to Attorney General
OL,6,FAmaaz was found guilty of assaulting
OL,7,Ftwo female officers during the
OL,8,Fconfrontation in July 2024 and is
OL,9,Fawaiting sentencing, but a third trial
OL,10,Fof the two men over the alleged
OL,11,Fassault on PC Zachary Marsden was
OL,12,Fruled out at Liverpool Crown Court on
OL,13,FFriday 29 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
